{"tid":980573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喝完能量飲料後GG勃起6小時　廠商急下架","createTime":"2019-01-13T15:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T16:54:55.000Z","uid":32511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"197ffe035ba68f5ebc06a80de1f31a0bcf46b045","tid":980573,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"烏干達一名男子，喝了一瓶名為「SX Energy Natural Power Drink」的能量飲料後，感覺的身體有異常，不僅會大量出汗、心跳異常外，他的GG還勃起了6小時。<br />\n <br />\n據《新聞週刊》(Newsweek)報導，測試後發現，這款能量飲料含有西地那非(Sildenafil)、是一種研發治療心血管疾病藥物時、意外發明出的治療男性勃起功能障礙藥物。該飲料的生產商是位於尚比亞的Revin Zambia，他們已經在8日停止生產開款能量飲料，公司總經理庫伯(Vikas Kappor)表示，歡迎政府或其他機構進行調查，「至少我們不知道這種飲料有任何有害成分」。<br />\n <br />\n除了西地那非之外，尚比亞醫藥學會還發現，這款飲料還有生薑、東革阿里、睪酮促進劑等成分。"},{"pid":"073a9b023d35d81dfc19bd04b90e567f0b44591d","tid":980573,"uid":78429,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"寫明SX Energy扯六個鐘有咩問題"},{"pid":"6f88da2d7b5c95d97d2b226ebc68fb19f936a1f8","tid":980573,"uid":89595,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"073a9b023d35d81dfc19bd04b90e567f0b44591d","tid":980573,"uid":78429,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"寫明SX Energy扯六個鐘有咩問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"驚太搶手"},{"pid":"61831533b52859fd368d7fc4ef555673e6825893","tid":980573,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"073a9b023d35d81dfc19bd04b90e567f0b44591d","tid":980573,"uid":78429,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"寫明SX Energy扯六個鐘有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"扯得太耐條丁會壞死"},{"pid":"10bbfef7a57c02ec52239c1c3fe41388e472b969","tid":980573,"uid":3932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"Wakanda?"},{"pid":"45e4aae4e08f2d769cd059e4c3f50ee1db0004bc","tid":980573,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"Sex ene